data.title: About: Sahasam (1992 film)
data.meta_description: Sahasam (transl. Adventure) is a 1992 Telugu-language action film, produced by M. V. Rao under the Sridevi Productions banner and directed by Suresh Krishna. It stars Jagapathi Babu, Bhanu Chander, Saranya, Kaveri and music composed by M. M. Keeravani.
